      <title>日本首都通胀率连续第二个月放缓，低于日本央行目标</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/inflation-japans-capital-falls-below-boj-target-slows-2nd-month-2024-04-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五数据显示，日本首都核心通胀 4 月份连续第二个月放缓，低于央行 2% 的目标，这使得央行加息决定变得更加复杂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/inflation-japans-capital-falls-below-boj-target-slows-2nd-month-2024-04-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 23:52:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行可能通过新的价格预测暗示近期加息</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/bank-japan-may-signal-near-term-rate-hike-with-new-price-forecasts-2024-04-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行周五预计，未来几年通胀率将保持在 2% 的目标附近，并表示准备将利率从接近于零的水平上调，以防止日元空头将日元推至 34 年来新低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/bank-japan-may-signal-near-term-rate-hike-with-new-price-forecasts-2024-04-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 22:25:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
