      <title>Cigna 将为 Humira 竞争对手在专业药房提供 0 美元自付额</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/cigna-offer-humira-rivals-with-0-copay-specialty-pharmacy-2024-04-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[健康保险公司周四表示，Cigna 计划从 6 月开始，通过其专业药房向美国符合条件的患者免费提供艾伯维 (AbbVie) 风靡关节炎药物修美乐 (Humira) 的仿制品，无需自付费用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/cigna-offer-humira-rivals-with-0-copay-specialty-pharmacy-2024-04-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 20:48:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
